                     <interp inst="t18390513-1523-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18390513-cd-49" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18390513-1523-offence-1 t18390513-cd-49"></join>4th of May</rs>, 1 handkerchief, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., and 1 snuff-box, value 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18390513-name-345" type="victimName">
